You're referring to Instagram's "Gift" feature. This feature allows creators to receive gifts from their followers during live streams. Gifts are a way for viewers to show their appreciation and support for their favorite creators. When a viewer sends a gift, it appears in the live stream, and the creator can acknowledge and thank them in real-time. Gifts can be purchased with Instagram's Stars, which are virtual tokens that can be bought within the app.
